title: Newbie looking for help :^) How to level up here on boards?
body: Hi, this place seems super cool! But I guess I cant really post anything before certain levels been achieved. Any good idea how to level up real quick? Feel like wanna be boosted :^)

replies.body:
Congrats, you've hit max level! Sometimes it takes a post like this to cause a sync to happen between your Boards and Summoner profiles.

Happy posting!
